s://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pink-fox-linabell-wins-chinese-hearts-disney-taps-emotional-economy-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>独家：比亚迪以非正常签证将数百名中国工人带到巴西</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/byd-brought-hundreds-chinese-workers-brazil-irregular-visas-inspector-2025-01-08/</link><description>一位重要的劳工监察员周二告诉路透社，电动汽车生产商比亚迪带着数百名持非正常签证的中国工人在巴西建厂，并补充说该公司已承诺对留在该国的工人遵守当地劳动法。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 00:50:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/byd-brought-hundreds-chinese-workers-brazil-irregular-visas-inspector-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>西藏地震幸存者搜寻工作日益紧迫</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/rescue-efforts-under-way-after-earthquake-tibet-kills-more-than-120-2025-01-08/</link><description>中国官员周三表示，西藏地震灾区有超过 400 名被困在废墟中的人获救，但地震震撼了喜马拉雅山麓并改变了该地区的地貌，仍有不明人数下落不明。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 00:35:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/rescue-efforts-under-way-after-earthquake-tibet-kills-more-than-120-2025-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>华盛顿对中国宁德时代的标签可能会对特斯拉产生怎样的影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-washingtons-tag-chinas-catl-could-affect-tesla-2025-01-07/</link><description>华盛顿将宁德时代列入与中国军方合作的公司名单，这可能会让特斯拉创始人埃隆·马斯克陷入困境，挑战他如何平衡自己在特朗普政府中的角色与与中国的关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 23:00:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/how-washingtons-tag-chinas-catl-could-affect-tesla-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>科技组织敦促美国停止限制全球获取人工智能芯片的规定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/tech-group-urges-us-halt-rule-that-would-limit-global-access-ai-chips-2025-01-07/</link><description>一个科技行业组织周二敦促总统乔·拜登政府不要在最后一刻发布控制全球人工智能芯片获取的规则，并警告称这些限制将危及美国在人工智能领域的领导地位。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 19:36:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/tech-group-urges-us-halt-rule-that-would-limit-global-access-ai-chips-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>谢因对中国棉花使用保持沉默，让英国立法者对供应链一无所知</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-representative-declines-say-if-company-uses-cotton-china-uk-hearing-2025-01-07/</link><description>周二，当英国议会委员会询问这家在线快时尚零售商是否使用来自中国或新疆省的棉花时，Shein 的代表拒绝提供直接答案，这对于担心其供应链的潜在投资者来说是一个关键问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 16:25:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/shein-representative-declines-say-if-company-uses-cotton-china-uk-hearing-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>汽车制造商将与特斯拉、Polestar 合并二氧化碳排放量，以满足欧盟 2025 年规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-toyota-ford-mazda-subaru-plan-pool-co2-emissions-with-tesla-2025-01-07/</link><description>电动汽车销量较低的公司可以与细分市场的领导者“汇集”其排放量。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 11:55:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-toyota-ford-mazda-subaru-plan-pool-co2-emissions-with-tesla-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国称美国对中国无人机存在安全风险的怀疑是“不负责任的”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-us-suspicion-security-risks-chinese-drones-is-irresponsible-2025-01-07/</link><description>中国商务部周二表示，中国称美国“毫无根据地怀疑”中国无人机系统存在信息安全风险，“极其不负责任”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 11:27:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-us-suspicion-security-risks-chinese-drones-is-irresponsible-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国奇瑞报告2024年销量增长38.4%至260万辆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-reports-384-jump-2024-sales-26-mln-vehicles-2025-01-07/</link><description>中国汽车制造商奇瑞 (CHERY.UL) 周二报告称，2024 年全球汽车销量将增长 38.4%，达到 260 万辆，并预计今年销量将超过 300 万辆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 10:39:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-chery-reports-384-jump-2024-sales-26-mln-vehicles-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国山东港是大多数受制裁石油的入境点，禁止美国指定的船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-shandong-port-group-blacklists-us-sanctioned-oil-vessels-say-traders-2025-01-07/</link><description>三名贸易商表示，山东港口集团已禁止美国制裁的油轮停靠中国东部省份的港口，该省是许多独立炼油厂的所在地，这些炼油厂是美国禁运国家石油的最大进口国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 09:07:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-shandong-port-group-blacklists-us-sanctioned-oil-vessels-say-traders-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>泰国官员称在缅甸失踪的中国演员可能是人口贩运受害者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-actor-missing-near-thai-myanmar-border-found-thai-officials-say-2025-01-07/</link><description>泰国当局周二表示，上周在泰缅边境附近失踪的一名中国演员已在缅甸找到，他可能是人口贩卖的受害者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 09:00:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-actor-missing-near-thai-myanmar-border-found-thai-officials-say-2025-01-07/</guid></item><item><title>前律师称中国新冠抗议电影制片人被判入狱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-covid-protest-filmmaker-sentenced-prison-former-lawyer-says-2025-01-07/</link><description>一名中国导演的前律师表示，一名拍摄了一部关于 2022 年“白皮书”示威活动、反对中国新冠疫情限制措施的中国导演，本周被上海一家法院判处三年半有期徒刑。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 08:45:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-covid-protest-filmmaker-sentenced-prison-former-lawyer-says-2025-01-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>